<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bump-v">bump <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bʌmp/    美 /bʌmp/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 撞击；碰撞：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Be careful not to <strong>bump</strong> your head <strong>on</strong> the low roof.
屋顶低，小心别碰头。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Su Hua and Li Jiang <strong>bumped into</strong> each other, trying to catch the ball.
苏华和李江在抢球的时候，撞到了一起。</p><footer>2012 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="bump-into">bump into</h3>
<p>1.<strong>［非正式用语］撞见；不期而遇 (run into)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Guess who I bumped into this afternoon?
你猜今天下午我撞见了谁？</p></div></div>